	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h2 class="no-left-margin">Share organising info</h2>
			<p>
				Upload and share collective bargaining agreements and company research.  Get in touch with key comrades from other unions, when agreements are expiring.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h2  class="no-left-margin">Chat securely and privately</h2>
			<p>
				Chat with officials from other unions about sensitive organising information without being at the mercy of organisations that fundamentally don't respect privacy.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-sm-4">
			<h2  class="no-left-margin">Organise globally</h2>
